Description:
This map is absoultely amazing, firstly it is a 'rats' style map (for those who dont know its where all the objects are oversized to make it look like your a rat). its themed as a room of a little girl, hence the name "de_dolls", now the attention to detail is what really impresses me, everything looks how it should, from the doll house to the Nemo poster on the wall, this is definately my map pick for the day.
